### ========================================
### EJEMPLOS COMPLETOS DE LA API
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api
### ========================================

### ========================================
### PACIENTES
### ========================================

### 1. Crear Paciente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/api/pacientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pacDni": "12345678",
  "nombre": "Juan Carlos",
  "apellidoPaterno": "Pérez",
  "apellidoMaterno": "García",
  "direccion": "Av. Principal 123, Lima",
  "telefono": "+51987654321",
  "imagen": null
}

### 2. Crear otro Paciente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/api/pacientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pacDni": "87654321",
  "nombre": "María Elena",
  "apellidoPaterno": "López",
  "apellidoMaterno": "Rodríguez",
  "direccion": "Jr. Los Olivos 789, Arequipa",
  "telefono": "+51912345678",
  "imagen": null
}

### 3. Listar todos los Pacientes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/api/pacientes?page=0&size=10

### 4. Obtener Paciente por DNI
GET http://localhost:8080/api/api/pacientes/dni/12345678

### 5. Actualizar Paciente
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/api/pacientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pacDni": "12345678",
  "nombre": "Juan Carlos",
  "apellidoPaterno": "Pérez",
  "apellidoMaterno": "García",
  "direccion": "Av. Principal 456, Lima - ACTUALIZADO",
  "telefono": "+51987654321",
  "imagen": null
}

